רדף משטרתי אחר אופנוע באזור אל-משהד, בעקבות דיווח על ירי לעבר בית. משפחת לואבנה הכחישה את מעורבות בנם באירוע הירי לעבר הבית, וציינה כי הוא קיבל את האופנוע ללא ידיעה על התקרית וברח מהמשטרה מתוך פחד.","case_narrative_en":"Iyad Lawabna died on Friday, July 17, 2025, succumbing to a gunshot wound inflicted by Israeli police officers. The shooting occurred during a police pursuit of a motorcycle in the Al-Mashhad area, following a report of gunfire targeting a house. Lawabna's family denied their son's involvement in the shooting incident at the house, stating that he received the motorcycle unaware of the incident and fled from the police out of fear.","review_status":"auto","pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2025-01-01_2025-12-31","enrichment_passes":0,"_pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2025-01-01_2025-12-31","run_id":"canonical","case_index":195}